lead_paragraph: The Texas Rangers moved their chips all in and the once high and mighty Yankees traded talent to build for the future on Monday as the Major League Baseball (MLB) trading deadline came to a dizzying end.

headline.print_headline: Texas Rangers Push Trade Chips In for Pennant Push at Deadline
